Package org.apache.sling.api.adapter

Interface Summary
Adaptable  
AdapterFactory The AdapterFactory interface defines the API for helpers which may be provided to enhance the adaptability of adaptable objects.
AdapterManager The AdapterManager defines the service interface for a manager for object adaption.
 

Class Summary
SlingAdaptable The SlingAdaptable class is an (abstract) default implementation of the Adaptable interface.
